# xplr

> Terminal-based file system explorer
> More information: https://xplr.dev

- Open a directory:

`xplr {directory value}`

- Focus on a file:

`xplr {file value}`

- Focus on a directory:

`xplr --force-focus {directory value}`

- Open a directory with specific files or directories selected:

`xplr {directory value} {string value: path/to/selected_file_or_directory1} {string value: path/to/selected_file_or_directory2}`
